HEADWORD: Suspectful
<hw>Sus*pect"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Apt to suspect or
mistrust; full of suspicion; suspicious; <as>as, to be
<ex>suspectful</ex> of the motives of others</as>.</def>
<au>Milton.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Sus*pect"ful*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

